				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">5 pets who hit for 40 or so each 
<br />

<br />
Compare this to 79 we had first...
<br />

<br />
( The smart kids know that 5 x 40 &gt; 79 )
<br />

<br />
The advantage of AoD is that if a mob turns to your AoD pets, it now needs to kill 5 mobs instead of one. Have you ever seen our WTD pet survive 5 rounds from any but the most trivial mobs?
<br />
( And also that you do more dmg )
<br />

<br />
The disadvantage, to keep the AA from being too overpowered is that you need 5 corpses for 5 pets.
<br />

<br />
- Xyrian</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
